  "text": "The macrobenthos (including the fiddler crab, polychaete, and gastropod compartments) P/B values were estimated based on the equation of [CITATION_1] , considering the maximum age for each group obtained from the literature and the maximum body mass for each group based on our database. The Q/B value was based on the equation proposed by [CITATION_2] . All information on the P/B and Q/B values estimated in the model were obtained from the literature (see Table S4 for the parameters, equations and references).",
